|Example.Gloss=khatami: This organization prog-can.present-3sg and should focal become to goal-pl long-indef ke Islam, revolution and nation honorable Iran have.imp ast-cop
|Example.English translation=
Khatami: This organization can and should become a center for the realization of the high objectives that Islam, Revolution and the honorable people of Iran have had
|Example.Provenance=http://www.irangreenvoice.com/article
|Example.Comments=The word "long=boland" has a different frame. It is used to refer to loud "loud voice" tall "tall person" and high "high elevation" and others
}}{{Example
|Example.Language=Persian
|Example.Text=انسان بی هدف به مقصد نهایی خود نمی رسد وبا داشتن هدف در زندگی مشترک جهت نیل به مقصد نهایی که همان خوشبختی وآرامش می باشد خواهند رسید
|Example.Gloss=Human goal-less to ultimate destination self neg-prog-reach-prest-3sg and with have-infin goal in life mutual direction toward ultimate destination that identical happiness and tranquility prog-be.prest-3sg will-3pl reach-pres-pefc
|Example.English translation=A person without goal will not reach his/her ultimate destination and by having a goal in his/her marriage, he/she will reach his/her ultimate destination which is happiness and tranquility
|Example.Provenance=http://www.sarachehnaz.blogfa.com
|Example.Comments=The frames for "goal" and " ultimate destination" evoke eachother and are usually used as pairs
